OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782389904
OL,3,CMother of dying toddler delayed 999
OL,4,Ccall, murder trial hears
OL,6,FThe mother of a seriously ill toddler
OL,7,Fwho had suffered sexual and physical
OL,8,Fabuse delayed calling 999 when her
OL,9,Fdaughter was dying because she knew
OL,10,Fshe would be questioned about what had
OL,11,Fhappened, a court heard.
OL,13,FIsabelle Welsh, two, was found to have
OL,14,Fsuffered 21 different broken bones in
OL,15,Fthe weeks before she died last
OL,16,FSeptember after collapsing at her home
OL,17,Fin Thornaby, Teesside, jurors were
OL,18,Ftold heard.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/11
