CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782389904
OL,3,CMother of dying toddler delayed 999
OL,4,Ccall, murder trial hears
OL,6,FHer mother Alexandra Walker, 25, and
OL,7,Fboyfriend Harrison Simpson, 22, deny
OL,8,Fmurder, sexual assault, allowing the
OL,9,Fdeath of a child and child cruelty.
OL,11,FRichard Wright KC, prosecuting, said
OL,12,Fthe day before Isabelle died from a
OL,13,Fsevere head injury, the defendants had
OL,14,Fbeen up late drinking and smoking
OL,15,Fcannabis.
OL,17,FWhile Walker stayed in bed the
OL,18,Ffollowing morning, Simpson was up and
OL,19,Fin sole care of the toddler, Teesside
OL,20,FCrown Court heard on Wednesday (24
OL,21,FJune).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782389904
OL,3,CMother of dying toddler delayed 999
OL,4,Ccall, murder trial hears
OL,6,FHe later put Isabelle to bed and
OL,7,Faround 3pm on 13 September, and
OL,8,FSimpson left the two-bedroom property.
OL,10,FMr Wright said that within 10 minutes,
OL,11,FWalker googled "why would my toddler
OL,12,Fbe bleeding".
OL,14,FInternal CCTV from her home recorded
OL,15,Fher saying "You're scaring me" and
OL,16,Fthen she googled "what should I do if
OL,17,Fmy child has blood in his stool".
OL,19,FAround this time, Walker went into the
OL,20,Fkitchen to smoke a cigarette, jurors
OL,21,Fwere told.
OL,26,@sD@POUtD@LO]wD@LOUwD@^O]xD@ROUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
