PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782389904
OL,3,CMother of dying toddler delayed 999
OL,4,Ccall, murder trial hears
OL,6,FMr Wright said: "It is absolutely
OL,7,Fobvious that by this time Isabelle is
OL,8,Fgravely ill.
OL,10,F"She is quite simply dying.
OL,12,F"And yet, despite the searches on
OL,13,FGoogle, Alexandra Walker does nothing."
OL,15,FAround an hour after Simpson left,
OL,16,FWalker called her stepfather and he
OL,17,Farrived at around 4.15pm and
OL,18,Fimmediately told her to call 999.
OL,26,@nD@QOUrD@AOUtD@AOUuD@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
