OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FEarlier that month, Walker had taken
OL,12,Fher daughter to hospital after
OL,13,FIsabelle suffered a broken tibia, and
OL,14,Fshe had explained the injury to medics
OL,15,Fas Isabelle hurting herself by poking
OL,16,Fher leg through the cot.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
