OL,3,CMother of dying toddler delayed 999
OL,4,Ccall, murder trial hears
OL,6,FOpening the case to the jury, Mr
OL,7,FWright said: "In due course you may
OL,8,Fwant to consider why there was very
OL,9,Fsignificant delay in summoning the
OL,10,Femergency services.
OL,12,F"One explanation of course is that
OL,13,FAlexandra Walker knew that this time
OL,14,Fshe would not be able to bluff and
OL,15,Fbluster her way out of the very
OL,16,Fdifficult questions that she knew she
OL,17,Fwould be asked at hospital."
OL,26,@oD@NOUtD@AOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/11
