OL,3,CMother of dying toddler delayed 999
OL,4,Ccall, murder trial hears
OL,6,FParamedics arrived within a minute and
OL,7,FIsabelle was rushed to hospital, but
OL,8,Fshe died in the early hours of the
OL,9,Fnext day.
OL,11,FWalker and Simpson were arrested and
OL,12,Fthe mother said her boyfriend was her
OL,13,Fnew partner, that they had been
OL,14,Ftogether for a month, and that she had
OL,15,Fraised concerns about bruises on
OL,16,FIsabelle's body but he had denied
OL,17,Fbeing responsible.
OL,19,FIn a separate, later interview, she
OL,20,Ftold police she now realised Simpson
OL,21,Fhad been abusing her daughter.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
