OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1782389904
OL,3,CMother of dying toddler delayed 999
OL,4,Ccall, murder trial hears
OL,6,FSimpson did not answer questions
OL,7,Fduring interviews, Mr Wright said.
OL,9,FHe told the court: "The prosecution
OL,10,Fwill invite you to conclude that
OL,11,FAlexandra Walker was telling lies and
OL,12,Fthat Harrison Simpson said nothing
OL,13,Fbecause he had no answer at all to the
OL,14,Fquestions that were being asked.
OL,16,F"They both knew exactly what had
OL,17,Fhappened to Isabelle because in the
OL,18,Fweeks before her death they had each
OL,19,Fsubjected her to violence culminating
OL,20,Fin the infliction of that terrible,
OL,21,Ffatal head injury.
OL,26,@qD@TOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
