OL,3,CMother of dying toddler delayed 999
OL,4,Ccall, murder trial hears
OL,6,FSimpson was in sole care of Isabelle
OL,7,Fat times in the weeks before her
OL,8,Fdeath, the court heard.
OL,10,FMr Wright said both defendants were
OL,11,Faware of what was happening to
OL,12,FIsabelle which would have been
OL,13,F"obvious".
OL,15,FHe said: "She was distressed, she was
OL,16,Funwell, deteriorating. These were not
OL,17,Fhidden events, they were not fleeting
OL,18,For isolated incidents.
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@IO]wD@JOU
