OL,3,CMother of dying toddler delayed 999
OL,4,Ccall, murder trial hears
OL,6,F"This was a pattern of abuse over
OL,7,Ftime, in a small house in the presence
OL,8,Fof both defendants."
OL,10,FWalker and Simpson deny all charges
OL,11,Fand the trial continues.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@TO]
